| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6172 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ca9ebdaf-bce4-5a74-b59a-e41e36d5cf76"
